      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i walk into the kitchen and i forget for a second that he isn't there, and then it hits me all over again. the house is so empty it feels like i'm living in a tomb. i don't even know why i'm bothering to wake up every morning. there's just nothing left.",
